name: Elemental Portal: Water
description: Piece created using sacred geometry and symbols with the intention of connecting directly with the deep all-knowing parts of your soul. This piece connects with the element of Water, bringing lightness, fluidity, adaptability and balance. Water connects with our emotional nature, allowing this aspect of ourselves to flow freely and in harmony, and is also related with creative expression and sexual energy, tapping into our unique potential to manifest our deepest desires with Love and Compassion.
